ğŸ”„ Maven vs. Gradle: A Detailed Comparison
ğŸ›  Which One Should You Choose?
âœ… Use Maven if you need stability, structured builds, and an easier learning curve. âœ… Use Gradle if you want faster builds, better performance, and flexibility for complex projects.
